|text= ''caller'' can only be [[player]] due to {{arma2}} design: FSM overrides by <sqf inline>_clicker = player</sqf> instead of <sqf inline>_clicker = _this select 0</sqf>).<br>
Parameters displayed are incorrect, these are:
<sqf>
_caller		= _this select 0;
_veh		= _this select 1;
_passedPos	= _this select 2;
_mainScope	= _this select 3;
_secopScope	= _this select 4;

if (count _this > 5) then
{
	_supportType = _this select 5;
